### How to run

#### 1. main test

```bash
sudo make uthread-sync-demo
sudo ./uthread-sync-demo <param1> <param2>
```

#### 2. lock vs spinlock (performance test)

```bash
sudo make lock-vs-spinlock
./lock-vs-spinlock <thread_num>
```

#### 3. sync vs async IO (performance test)

```bash
sudo make sync-vs-async
sudo ./sync-vs-async <io_thread_num> <io_rw_len> <comp_thread_num> <comp_work_load>
```

#### 4. priority inversion

```bash
sudo make priority-inversion
./priority-inversion
```

#### 5. test zoo (functional test: lock & condvar)

```bash
sudo make test-zoo
./test-zoo <animal_num>
```

#### 6. test Async IO (functional test: async_io)

```bash
sudo make test-async-io
sudo ./test-async-io
```

### Performance

Performance test results and test details are included in the report.pdf.